      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"section\"><h3 id=\"Upgradingto2.2-DownTime\">Down Time</h3><p>The time required to upgrade the job database depends on the number of existing jobs in the database and the CPU and I/O speed of the host. In our test, a job database with 700,000 jobs was upgraded in under 2 minutes; the host had 2.8GHz CPUs and a 7200 RPM HDD.</p><p> </p></div><div class=\"section\"><h3 id=\"Upgradingto2.2-Other\">Other</h3><p>Please refer to the standard upgrade instructions described in <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/TRA/pages/22184348/Upgrading\" data-linked-resource-id=\"22184348\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Upgrading</a>.</p></div>"
    }
